extends BaseReport<ResultSearchParameters,SummaryReportRow>

    Encapsulates Summary Report data.

    The references in this class cannot be changed, but it is not truly immutable because ResultSearchParameters is mutable.

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.
